{"type": "article", "id": 20536, "title": "69 岁的传奇音乐人大卫·鲍威去世", "description": "这位多才多艺的艺术家在与癌症搏斗了一年半之后去世", "date": "2016-01-11T16:01:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 594, "name": "纽约时报"}, {"id": 21691, "name": "DAVID BOWIE"}], "category": 5, "author": 18, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143731l2MK6Gti9gz4xpYr.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>周一，据大卫</span><span>·</span><span>鲍威（<span><a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/b/david_bowie/index.html?inline=nyt-per%2522%2520%255Co%2520%2522More%2520articles%2520about%2520David%2520Bowie.%2522%2520%255Ct%2520%2522_blank\">David Bowie</a>，也有译作<span>大卫</span><span>·</span><span>鲍伊</span></span>）的公关人员称，这位传奇音乐人已经去世。此前在 </span><span>Facebook </span><span>和 </span><span>Twitter </span><span>上都出现了关于他去世的报道，周一上午，这位名叫斯蒂夫</span><span>·</span><span>马丁（</span><span>Steve Martin</span><span>）的公关人员确认了此事。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>马丁并没有说他因何而死，但鲍威 </span><span>Facebook </span><span>页面上的<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/davidbowie/posts/10153176666977665\"><span>一份声明</span></a>称，他是在与癌症搏斗了一年半之后去世的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这位多才多艺的艺术家最后一张专辑《</span><span>Blackstar</span><span>》周五刚刚发布</span><span>——</span><span>那天也是他的生日。人们原定于 </span><span>3 </span><span>月 </span><span>31 </span><span>日在卡内基音乐厅举办一场音乐会来表示对鲍威的尊敬，出席音乐会的音乐人包括 </span><span>The Roots</span><span> 、辛迪</span><span>·</span><span>劳帕（</span><span>Cyndi Lauper</span><span>）和</span><span> Mountain Goats</span><span> 。鲍威的音乐剧《拉撒路》（<a href=\"http://nyti.ms/1Hub954%2522%2520%255Ct%2520%2522_blank\"><span>Lazarus</span></a>）也正在百老汇上演。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>鲍威于 </span><span>1947 </span><span>年 </span><span>1 </span><span>月 </span><span>8 </span><span>日出生于伦敦南部，原名大卫</span><span>·</span><span>琼斯（</span><span>David Jones</span><span>）。</span><span>1969 </span><span>年，他凭借专辑《太空怪人》（</span><span>Space Oddity</span><span>）而成名，后来他在专辑《</span><span>Ziggy Stardust</span><span>》中穿着连体衫的另一个自我也震惊世人。</span><span>1996 </span><span>年，他<a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/1996/01/18/arts/new-inductees-into-the-rock-hall-of-fame.html\"><span>进入了摇滚名人堂</span></a>。据路透社称，</span><span>2006 </span><span>年纽约的一场慈善音乐会是他的最后一次现场演出。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>翻译：熊猫译社 葛仲君</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图版权：Leonhard Foeger/路透社\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}